{"tid":1103331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺係公車睇書好造作？","createTime":"2019-04-12T10:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T10:46:19.000Z","uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"616fc6c94f6997ac1750b103b8969c5a4f4ee012","tid":1103331,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"好心D人唔好扮晒野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55645a4738dc47f9870d897b8d25b094fd1c8d02","tid":1103331,"uid":133301,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:29:47.000Z","msg":"乜撚野公車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a95c73b45a05c2a762f02dd34d891799ade8680","tid":1103331,"uid":94828,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"55645a4738dc47f9870d897b8d25b094fd1c8d02","tid":1103331,"uid":133301,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:29:47.000Z","msg":"乜撚野公車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:30:58.000Z","msg":"公車上書，即公車孝廉連署上書，指康有為於清朝光緒二十一年（1895年）率同梁啓超等公車孝廉聯名向北京的光緒皇帝上書，反對在甲午戰爭中敗於日本的清政府簽訂喪權辱國的《馬關條約》。此舉被認為是維新派登上歷史舞台的標誌，也被認為是中國群眾的政治運動的開端。<br />\n<br />\n如茅海建等不少學者則考証許多文獻表示，康有為所謂的組織「公車孝廉連署上書」，事實上，只是一次自吹自擂的事件，只有八十個舉人參加連署，而非康有為所稱的一千多人。而當時僅僅一名廣東舉人陳景華的上書都有兩百八十人的連署，遠勝康有為。其實當時也有真正成功的上書，實由當時的翁同龢、李鴻藻、汪鳴鑾等京城高官發動組織，目的是阻撓《馬關條約》的簽訂。"},{"pid":"123a37d955a8f253020e302f5328dcf74f436045","tid":1103331,"uid":52942,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:33:53.000Z","msg":"車公雖然係武官，但係關公都睇書啦，人地唔睇多d兵書點打仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8020a4a36ca668f729bba7844439443a597f6a7","tid":1103331,"uid":52658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:36:05.000Z","msg":"我都睇錯左做公車上書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c38e11f178fcb0fa2cab38fbaf60d4b727aaa7","tid":1103331,"uid":210114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:38:38.000Z","msg":"老鐵牛逼666666😂🤙🏻🤙🏻🤙🏻"},{"pid":"d2a2999bc0f1b05717408c3c26c3b2f514b9d037","tid":1103331,"uid":225760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:38:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dbf79814d1f8e93f8ed779c2ee92b5a2eeeccfa","tid":1103331,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:42:03.000Z","msg":"今朝先係地鐵見倒個米9鬼佬著西裝懶係斯文 咁 仲要睇英文書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219a45dc51597266a785f1340f0044923e447943","tid":1103331,"uid":211914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:45:52.000Z","msg":"公你老母車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deef90d322658488bc48138e7a34ccf0e2ace168","tid":1103331,"uid":217476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:46:19.000Z","msg":"睇錯公車上書+1"}]}